assignmentevaluator.evaluationHelpers.executors.programlevel.CompileTestExecutor
public class CompileTestExecutor extends assignmentevaluator.evaluationHelpers.executors.programlevel.ProgramTestExecutor
This class is responsible for executing the compilation test for a program. It evaluates whether the program compiles successfully and generates feedback based on the result.
